title: VonZipper  : Hana Beaman in the Chakra
description: The maximum in minimalism, this goggle is a ritual in oneness with the flow of the flurry universe. The Chakra will help you find your spiritual center of snow unity sending you down the blizzardy path of meaningful existence.
